name: STROLIXED CYBER 2069
description:
STROLIXED CYBER 2069 Controls

There's no W and S because you only move forward.

Press space to jump


Press A and D to move left or right


Click to shoot(You won't need it)

Summary of the game

This is the hardest game you will ever play. This platformer game consist of 3 levels and each level it will get harder.The first person to win the whole game and sent it to my gmail will receive every single one of my game free for life.
PLAY IT IF YOU HAVE STOMACH FOR IT!
